        <font color="white" face="Verdana, Arial, Helvetica" size="2">heh calling bards the emergency patch pet is kind of ironic.  There was a time when any significant patch broke something with bards.  Couldn't proc while singing, couldn't keep levitate up for more than one cycle, couldn't use items while moving, group haste turns to group slow (boggle), etc.  Maybe they thought 'oh crap we did it again' and went out of their way this time.</P><P>Historically, "bugs" that make the game easier get the fastest attention.  It's standard policy for games like this (EQ wasn't unique even at release), to prevent casual exploiting.</P><P>But with SoL out this bug is long overdue in fixing.</P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height=15 width=15 border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
